  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "t42RdR51qenR2OkTphdWF6q96Ts=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# service-offering model defines tiered pricing with option groups and service groups\n\n`powerhouse/service-offering` is the central document model in this project. It manages a complete service catalog with tiered pricing.\n\n## State Shape\n\n```graphql\ntype ServiceOfferingState {\n    id: PHID!\n    operatorId: PHID!              # \u2192 BuilderProfile (external)\n    resourceTemplateId: PHID       # \u2192 ResourceTemplate\n    title: String!\n    summary: String!\n    status: ServiceStatus!         # DRAFT | COMING_SOON | ACTIVE | DEPRECATED\n    availableBillingCycles: [BillingCycle!]!\n    targetAudiences: [TargetAudience!]!\n    facetTargets: [FacetTarget!]!\n    facetBindings: [ResourceFacetBinding!]!\n    serviceGroups: [ServiceGroup!]!\n    services: [Service!]!\n    tiers: [ServiceSubscriptionTier!]!\n    optionGroups: [OptionGroup!]!\n    finalConfiguration: FinalConfiguration\n}\n```\n\n## Modules (7)\n\n| Module | Operations | Purpose |\n|--------|-----------|---------|\n| offering | 14 | Core metadata, operator, resource template, audiences, facets, billing cycles |\n| services | 5 | Add/update/delete services, facet bindings |\n| tiers | 12 | Tier CRUD, service levels, usage limits, billing cycle discounts, pricing mode |\n| option-groups | 10 | Option group CRUD, standalone/tier-dependent pricing, discount mode |\n| service-groups | 10 | Service group CRUD, tier pricing, setup costs, recurring price options |\n| configuration | 2 | Set/clear final configuration (resolved pricing snapshot) |\n\n## Key Internal References\n\n- `Service.serviceGroupId: OID` \u2192 ServiceGroup (groups services)\n- `Service.optionGroupId: OID` \u2192 OptionGroup (links service to option group)\n- `ServiceGroupTierPricing.tierId: OID` \u2192 ServiceSubscriptionTier\n- `OptionGroupTierPricing.tierId: OID` \u2192 ServiceSubscriptionTier\n- `ServiceLevelBinding.serviceId: OID` \u2192 Service\n- `ServiceUsageLimit.serviceId: OID` \u2192 Service\n\n## External References\n\n- `operatorId: PHID` \u2192 BuilderProfile (external Powerhouse model)\n- `resourceTemplateId: PHID` \u2192 ResourceTemplate (this project)\n- `facetBindings.facetType: PHID` \u2192 Facet (this project)\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[schema design]]\n- [[object relations]]\n- [[architecture decisions]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z"
    }
  },
